## Understanding the Badges

* The badge code at a high level looks like this:
`
  [![hover-text](badge-code)](OPERATIONS-ENGINEERING-REPORT-URL#REPO-NAME "Link to report")
`

* The badge code can be broken into these sections:
`
  https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/ json ?color=blue &style=for-the-badge &logo=github &label=MoJ-Compliant &query=OPERATIONS-ENGINEERING-REPORT-JSON-DATA-PATH &url=OPERATIONS-ENGINEERING-REPORT-URL
`

* See the [shields.io](https://shields.io/) page to understand each section above or to make modifications.
